fields.title: Wine Tasting
fields.description: An expert sommelier will teach the group about the wines offered at each vineyard visited.

fields.title: Vineyard Tour
fields.description: A staff member will show the group a tour of the vineyard from vine to cask at each vineyard visited.

fields.title: Hay Ride
fields.description: A ride around the hills of Sonoma.

fields.title: Trail Hike
fields.description: Hike the Glen Canyon Park Trail as a group!

fields.title: Toyosu Market
fields.description: Visit the market that replaced the Tsukiji Market to learn about different fish and produce available in Japan!

fields.title: National Museum of Nature and Science
fields.description: Explore the wonders of Tokyo's National Museum of Nature and Science with your little one(s).

fields.title: Shinjuku Gyoen National Garden
fields.description: Japan is famous for its intricate and perfectly-crafted gardens. On this trip, we will explore the Shinjuku Gyoen National Garden, arguably the most beautiful garden in the world!

fields.title: Art Walk
fields.description: A tour of the famous art galleries and murals around Santa Fe

fields.title: Meow Wolf
fields.description: Come explore one of the wildest and most interactive art exhibits in the world, filled with incredible color and creativity.

fields.title: Jewelry-Making Class
fields.description: Enjoy a three-hour jewelry making class with one of Taos' most renowned artists.

fields.title: Tequila Tasting
fields.description: Enjoy a tasting of an array of tequilas made in New Mexico and the surraounding areas.
